      "title": "Loans and aid given by India to Sri Lanka in 2022. Exceeds 4",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Indian High Commission in Sri Lanka, the value of loans and aid provided by India to Sri Lanka, which is facing a severe economic crisis, has exceeded 4 billion US dollars.",
        "With the official delivery of 21,000 metric tons of the last stock of 65,000 metric tons of urea given to Sri Lanka under Indian loan assistance, the Indian loan and aid has exceeded 4 billion dollars."
